# Mac File Organizer Web App
A full-stack Python application that automatically sorts messy Downloads folders into categorized sub-folders (Images, Documents, Music, etc.).

## Features
- **One-Click Organization**: Instantly sort your Mac's Downloads folder.
- **Visual Feedback**: View a detailed list of every file moved on a success page.
- **Web Interface**: Built with Flask for a clean, user-friendly experience.

## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Python (Flask)
- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3
- **Automation**: Shutil and Pathlib libraries